C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20the%20ANI%2C%20Ms%20Bharti%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20introduction%20of%20the%20women's%20reservation%20Bill%20in%20the%20parliament%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20happiness%20for%20the%20women%20of%20the%20country.%20When%20this%20special%20reservation%20was%20presented%20in%20the%20House%20by%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Deve%20Gowda%20in%201996%2C%20I%20was%20a%20member%20of%20Parliament.%20I%20immediately%20stood%20up%20and%20moved%20an%20amendment%20to%20this%20Bill%20and%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20House%20supported%20me.%20Deve%20Gowda%20happily%20accepted%20the%20amendment.%20He%20announced%20the%20handing%20over%20of%20the%20Bill%20to%20the%20Standing%20Committee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20uproar%20in%20the%20House%20before%20it%20was%20adjourned.%20As%20soon%20as%20she%20came%20to%20the%20corridor%20of%20the%20House%2C%20many%20MPs%20from%20her%20party%20were%20angry%20but%20late%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20gave%20her%20a%20patient%20listening.%20Despite%20being%20staunch%20political%20opponents%2C%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20Lalu%20Yadav%2C%20and%20their%20party%20MPs%20were%20all%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20amendment%2C%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20in%20her%20letter%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20presenting%20a%20proposal%20for%20an%20amendment%20before%20you%20(PM%20Modi)%20as%20well.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20you%20will%20get%20this%20Bill%20passed%20with%20the%20proposed%20amendments.%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20legislative%20bodies%20is%20a%20special%20provision.%20However%2C%20it%20should%20be%20ensured%20that%20of%20these%2033%20per%20cent%20reserved%20seats%2C%2050%20per%20cent%20are%20set%20aside%20for%20ST%2C%20SC%20and%20OBC%20women.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20provision%20for%20special%20reservations%20for%20backward%20caste%20women%20in%20Panchayati%20Raj%20and%20local%20bodies%2C%20she%20noted%20in%20her%20letter%2C%20adding%20that%20backward%20women%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20recognised%20as%20such%20by%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%2C%20should%20also%20be%20considered%20for%20reservation%20in%20legislative%20bodies.%20If%20this%20Bill%20is%20passed%20without%20this%20special%20provision%2C%20then%20the%20women%20from%20the%20backward%20classes%20will%20be%20deprived%20of%20this%20special%20opportunity%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20the%20MPs%20of%20our%20party%20and%20other%20parties%2C%20especially%20the%20Left%20and%20Congress%20MPs%2C%20were%20very%20angry%20with%20me%2C%20some%20senior%20leaders%20of%20our%20party%20supported%20me.%20As%20long%20as%20I%20was%20with%20you%20in%20the%20cabinet%20for%20five%20years%2C%20whenever%20the%20issue%20of%20women's%20reservation%20was%20raised%2C%20I%20would%20insist%20that%20it%20should%20be%20balanced%20and%20holistic%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Bharti%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20no%20longer%20in%20the%20Parliament%20but%20the%20backward%2C%20Dalit%20and%20tribal%20sections%20of%20the%20country%20are%20confident%20that%20our%20government%20will%20clear%20the%20Bill%20after%20taking%20interests%20into%20consideration%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Women%20Quota%20Bill%2C%20which%20provides%20for%2033%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20well%20as%20the%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%2C%20cleared%20its%20final%20legislative%20hurdle%20at%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Thursday%20with%20214%20members%20voting%20in%20support%20and%20none%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Bill%20got%20the%20nod%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20it%20was%20passed%20with%20a%20brute%20majority%20of%20454%20votes%20in%20favour%20and%20just%202%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20some%20Opposition%20members%20flagged%20concerns%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20implementation%20o