ead%20coach%2C%20is%20under%20focus%20ahead%20of%20the%202023%20ODI%20Cricket%20World%20Cup.%20India%20have%20not%20won%20the%20marquee%20event%20since%20the%202011%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E's%20men%20won%20the%20trophy%20after%20a%20great%20title%20clash%20against%20Sri%20Lanka.%20Rahul%20Dravid%2C%20who%20himsekd%20has%20been%20part%20of%20several%20Cricket%20World%20Cups%20as%20a%20player%2C%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20guiding%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E-led%20team%20to%20the%20ultimate%20glory.%20If%20Rahul%20Dravid%20can%20help%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20win%20the%202023%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20as%20a%20coach%2C%20it%20will%20add%20another%20glorious%20chapter%20to%20his%20already%20illustrious%20career.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20Dravid%20family%20household%20had%20a%20good%20news.%20Dravid's%20son%20Samit%20has%20been%20selected%20for%20Karnataka's%2015-member%20squad%20for%20the%20upcoming%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Vinoo%20Mankad%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41126-mulwantrai-himatlal-mankad-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVinoo%20Mankad%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trophy%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Fcricket%2Fdomestic%2Frahul-dravid-son-samit-karnataka-squad-vinoo-mankad-trophy-2023-under19%2Farticle67338398.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESportstar%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20U-19%20tournament%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Hyderabad%20from%20October%2012%20to%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20head%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20have%20been%20rested%20as%20the%20team%20wanted%20them%20to%20be%20fresh%20mentally%20and%20physically%20for%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%20India%20will%20take%20on%20Australia%20in%20a%20three-match%20ODI%20series%2C%20starting%20from%20the%20first%20ODI%20at%20Mohali%20on%20Thursday.%20It%20will%20be%20India's%20final%20assignment%20before%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20at%20home%20from%20October%205%20onwards.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20one%20of%20those%20series%2C%20where%20you%20have%20seen%20that%20some%20of%20our%20boys%20are%20not%20playing%20the%20first%20two%20games.%20We%20will%20rotate%20our%20pacers%20a%20bit.%20It%20will%20be%20nice%20for%20some%20other%20guys%20that%20they%20are%20given%20this%20opportunity%20to%20play%20three%20tough%20games%20before%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dravid%20in%20a%20pre-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20with%20people%20like%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%2C%20from%20our%20perspective%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20they%20reach%20the%20first%20game%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20with%20the%20physical%20and%20mental%20headspace%20they%20want%20to%20be%20in.%20With%20the%20amount%20of%20cricket%20they%20have%20played%2C%20they%20know%20how%20to%20prepare%20themselves%20for%20these%20big%20games.%20A%20lot%20of%20these%20decisions%20are%20discussed%20with%20them.%20We%20discuss%20with%20them%20how%20they%20would%20like%20to%20prepare%20leading%20up%20to%20big%20events.%20Based%20on%20these%20discussions%2C%20we%20come%20up%20with%20these%20mutual%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20return%20of%20spin-bowling%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1109-ravichandran-ashwin-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavichandran%20Ashwin%3C%2