%20House%20Collapses%20Due%20To%20Landslide%20In%20Uttarakhand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20house%20was%20seen%20collapsing%20due%20to%20a%20landslide%20in%20a%20terrifying%20video%20from%20Uttarakhand%20today.%20Several%20areas%20in%20Nainital%20were%20hit%20by%20the%20landslides%20early%20this%20morning%20due%20to%20which%20cracks%20appeared%20in%20various%20houses.%20The%20cracks%20gradually%20widened%20leading%20to%20the%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20the%20two-storey%20house%20was%20seen%20sliding%20down%20a%20slope%20and%20collapsing%20to%20the%20ground%20with%20a%20loud%20thud.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20casualties%20as%20the%20house%2C%20with%20around%20a%20dozen%20rooms%2C%20was%20vacated%20ahead%20of%20the%20accident.%20The%20surrounding%20houses%20in%20Nainital's%20Mallital%20area%20are%20also%20being%20evacuated%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERain-related%20disasters%20have%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20111%20people%20and%20affected%2045%2C650%20families%20in%20Uttarakhand%20this%20year%2C%20the%20state%20assembly%20was%20told%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Premchand%20Agarwal%20said%20natural%20disasters%20triggered%20by%20heavy%20rain%20led%20to%20the%20deaths%20of%20111%20people%20and%20injuries%20to%2072.%20The%20disasters%20also%20affected%2045%2C650%20families%2C%20who%20have%20been%20granted%20financial%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2030.40%20crore%2C%20he%20said%2C%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20by%20Opposition%20members%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFlooding%20and%20landslides%20are%20common%20and%20cause%20widespread%20devastation%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season%2C%20but%20experts%20say%20climate%20change%20is%20increasing%20their%20frequency%20and%20severity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EScientists%20blame%20a%20clash%20of%20weather%20systems%20triggered%20by%20global%20warming%20for%20the%20torrential%20rains%20this%20monsoon%20season%20that%20have%20battered%20the%20country's%20Himalayan%20states%20-%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%20-%20killing%20hundreds%20and%20causing%20damages%20worth%20crores%20of%20rupees%20this%20monsoon%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERains%20hit%20the%20two%20states%20following%20the%20convergence%20of%20the%20monsoon%20system%20with%20Western%20Disturbances%2C%20a%20weather%20system%20that%20originates%20in%20the%20Mediterranean%20Sea%20and%20moves%20east%2C%20bringing%20moisture-laden%20winds%20that%20cause%20winter%20rain%20and%20snow%20in%20the%20Himalayas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThink%20of%20it%20as%20a%20collision%20of%20two%20forceful%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kuldeep%20Srivastava%2C%20head%20of%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department's%20regional%20centre%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20causes%20significant%20rain%20or%20even%20cloudbursts%20...%20we%20are%20noticing%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20intense%20spells%20of%20rain%20lasting%20short%20durations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20very%20heavy%20to%20extremely%20heavy%20rainfall%20days%20per%20decade%20in%20India's%20Himalayan%20states%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20(HP)%20and%20neighbouring%20Uttarakhand%20increased%20to%20118%20between%202011%20and%202020%20from%2074%20in%20the%20preceding%20decade%2C%20data%20from%20the%20weather%20office%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20monsoon%20brings%20South%20Asia%20around%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20annual%20rainfall%20and%20is%20vital%20for%20both%20agriculture%20and%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20millions.%20But%20it%20also%20brings%20destruction%20every%20year%20in%20the%20form%20of%20landslides%20and%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695486420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F8iolofpg_nainital-house-collapse-ndtv_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-2-storey-house-collapses-due-to-landslide-in-uttar