t-3.07.06-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29150739%2FScreenshot-2023-05-29-at-3.07.06-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29150739%2FScreenshot-2023-05-29-at-3.07.06-PM-300x167.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F29150739%2FScreenshot-2023-05-29-at-3.07.06-PM-1024x568.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-655467%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22666%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIn%20Bishenpur%20villages%20on%20Saturday%2C%C2%A0The%20Wire%C2%A0met%20small%20teams%20of%20Meitei%20men%2C%20armed%20with%20double-barrel%20guns%20and%20bullets%2C%20to%20chase%20away%20Kukis.%20Photo%3A%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20such%20a%20warning%20has%20been%20issued.%20On%20June%201%2C%20during%20his%20visit%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%2C%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20had%20also%20called%20for%20the%20surrender%20of%20illegal%20weapons.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20those%20who%20have%20weapons%2C%20I%20appeal%20to%20them%20to%20surrender%20the%20weapons%20before%20the%20police.%20Starting%20tomorrow%2C%20the%20police%20will%20start%20combing%20operations%20to%20find%20the%20weapons.%20If%20the%20police%20find%20the%20weapons%20from%20them%20during%20the%20combing%20operation%2C%20they%20will%20be%20dealt%20with%20strictly%20under%20stringent%20sections%20of%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20thousands%20of%20weapons%20have%20been%20stolen%20by%20locals%20in%20Manipur%2C%20as%20detailed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%20%3C%2Fem%3EOn%20May%203%2C%20when%20the%20violence%20began%20in%20Manipur%2C%20500%20guns%20and%20hundreds%20of%20ammunition%20had%20been%20looted%20by%20Kuki%20miscreants%20from%20N.%20Ibomcha%E2%80%99s%20gun%20house.%20Ibomcha%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20gun%20house%2C%20had%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Imphal%20Police%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20May%208%2C%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20in%20his%20first%20press%20conference%20since%20the%20violence%20began%20in%20Manipur%2C%20had%20said%20that%20miscreants%20had%20snatched%201%2C041%20weapons%20and%207%2C460%20ammunition%20from%20security%20forces%20during%20the%20riot%20since%20May%203%2C%20and%20over%20800%20of%20those%20still%20remain%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2027%2C%202023%2C%20a%20few%20Meitei%20defending%20their%20village%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20camera%20that%20some%20of%20them%20have%20unlicensed%20guns.%20The%20story%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9No2LcUGLwA%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20YouTube%20channel%20on%20June%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fwatch-weapons-in-the-shadows-a-glimpse-into-violence-in-manipur%5C%22%3EWatch%20%7C%20Weapons%20in%20the%20Shadows%3A%20A%20Glimpse%20Into%20Violence%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2029%2C%20a%20similar%20appeal%2C%20like%20the%20latest%20one%20by%20Singh%2C%20was%20made%20to%20the%20citizens%20to%20return%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20looted%20from%20armed%20police%20battalions%20and%20police%20stations%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%20or%20legal%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLegal%20action%20as%20per%20the%20Arms%20Act%201959%20and%20Rules%20will%20be%20taken%20in%20case%20any%20person%20is%20found%20to%20be%20in%20unauthorized%20and%20illegal%20possession%20of%20arms%20and%20ammunition%20during%20combing%20operations%20by%20security%20personnel%20or%20otherwise%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20announcement%20by%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%20was%20made%20when%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20was%20present%20in%20Manipur.%20During%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20presence%20in%20the%20state%2C%20nearly%203%2C000%20weapons%20were%20looted%20again%20in%20the%20state.%20Most%20weapons%20were%20looted%20from%20police%20camps%20and%20armories%20in%20the%20capital%20city%20of%20Imphal.%20As%20the%20violence%20entered%20its%20second%20month%2C%20nearly%20100%20people%20were%20killed%2C%20and%20more%20than%20300%20people%20were%20injured%20in%20this%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFirst%20information%20reports%20(FIRs)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-looted-weaponry-yet-to-return-to-police-armouries-cm-appeals-afresh-for-surrender%5C%22%3Eexamined%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20indicate%20the%20loot%20of%20sophisticated%20weapons%20like%20AK%20and%20Insas%20rifles%2C%20bombs%2C%20among%20others.%20Miscreants%20also%20took%20away%20bulletproof%20jackets%20and%20set%20fire%20to%20police%20stations%20while%20Manipur%20chief%20minister%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20for%20one%20more%20time%2C%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20on%20Monday%2C%20June%2019%2C%20to%20surrender%20arms%20that%20had%20been%20looted%20from%20police%20armories%20ever%20since%20the%20violence%20erupted%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Manipur%20minister%2C%20L.%20Susindro%20Meitei%2C%20had%20installed%20a%20drop%20box%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Khurai%2C%20Imphal%20East%2C%20inviting%20people%20to%20return%20the%20weapons%20looted%20or%20snatched%20from%20the%20police.%20An%208ft%20by%204ft%20banner%20put%20up%20in%20front%20of%20the%20drop%20box%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20four%20feet%20long%2C%20three-and-a-half%20feet%20wide%2C%20and%20five%20feet%20tall%20%E2%80%93%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20drop%20your%20snatched%20weapons%20here%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CFeel%20free%20to%20do%20so.%E2%80%9D%20The%20DropBox%20was%20set%20up%20in%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20response%20to%20a%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20appeal%20filed%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-gun-licenses-biren-singh-violence%5C%22%3Erevealed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%20the%20past%20seven%20years%2C%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20has%20issued%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20gun%20licenses%20in%20the%20Northeast.%20Data%20obtained%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20under%20RTI%20shows%20that%20there%20are%2035%2C117%20active%20gun%20licenses%20in%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20up%20from%2026%2C836%20in%20December%202016.%20Furthermore%2C%20in%20August%2C%20another%20loot%20took%20place%20at%20the%20second%20Indian%20Reserve%20Battalion%20at%20Narasena.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695484852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsurrender-illegal-weapons-in-15-days-or-face-action-manipur-cm-warns-people%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thousands%20of%20sophisticated%20weapons%20have%20been%20looted%20from%20state%20armouries%20and%20police%20stations%2C%20which%20rival%20groups%20used%20in%20unleashing%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%20Several%20such%20calls%20for%20surrendering%20weapons%20were%20also%20made%20in%20the%20past%2C%20but%20to%20no%20avail.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsurrender-illegal-weapons-in-15-days-or-face-action-manipur-cm-warns-people%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Finance%20Minister%20Sitharaman%20meets%20G20%20expert%20group%20on%20strengthening%20of%20MDBs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695483514000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Fmisc%2F2022-06%2F07%2Ffull%2Fnirmala-sitharaman-1654593594-92383100.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Ffinance-minister-sitharaman-meets-g20-expert-group-on-strengthening-of-mdbs-123092300853_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20on%20Saturday%20met%20the%20G20%20Independent%20Expert%20Group%20on%20strengthening%20of%20Multilateral%20Development%20Banks%20(MDBs).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Ffinance-minister-sitharaman-meets-g20-expert-group-on-strengthening-of-mdbs-123092300853_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP-Linked%20Group%20ABVP%20Wins%20Big%20At%20Delhi%20University%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20RSS-affiliated%20ABVP%20on%20Saturday%20won%20three%20out%20of%20the%20four%20central%20panel%20posts%20of%20the%20Delhi%20University%20Students%20Union%20(DUSU)%20and%20the%20Congress'%20student%20wing%20NSUI%20bagged%20one%2C%20according%20to%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETushar%20Dedha%20of%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%20won%20the%20post%20of%20DUSU%20president%2C%20defeating%20NSUI's%20Hitesh%20Gulia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20student%20wing's%20Abhi%20Dahiya%20bagged%20the%20post%20of%20vice-president.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EABVP's%20Aparajita%20and%20Sachin%20Baisla%20won%20the%20posts%20of%20secretary%20and%20joint%20secretary%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20counting%20of%20votes%20for%20the%20DUSU's%20central%20panel%20posts%20of%20president%2C%20vice-president%2C%20secretary%20and%20joint%20secretary%20concluded%20on%20Saturday%20evening.%20The%20election%20was%20held%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20DUSU%20elections%20have%20always%20seen%20a%20direct%20fight%20between%20the%20ABVP%20and%20the%20National%20Students'%20Union%20of%20India%20(NSUI).%20The%20ABVP%20won%20three%20of%20the%20four%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20elections%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20DUSU%20elections%20were%20last%20held%20in%202019.%20The%20polls%20could%20not%20be%20held%20in%202020%20and%202021%20due%20to%20COVID-19%20while%20possible%20disruptions%20to%20the%20academic%20calendar%20prevented%20their%20conduct%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwenty-four%20candidates%20were%20in%20the%20fray%20for%20the%20four%20posts%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChander%20Shekhar%20--%20the%20chief%20election%20officer%20for%20the%20polls%20--%20said%20the%20university%20recorded%20a%20voter%20turnout%20of%2042%20per%20cent.%20Around%20one%20lakh%20students%20were%20eligible%20to%20vote%20in%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20voting%20percentage%20was%20higher%20than%20in%202019%20when%20a%20turnout%20of%2039.90%20per%20cent%20was%20recorded%2C%20it%20failed%20to%20surpass%20the%20nearly%2011-year-high%20figure%20of%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20turnouts%20in%202018%20and%202017%20were%2044.46%20per%20cent%20and%2042.8%20per%20cent%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElections%20at%2052%20colleges%20and%20departments%20for%20the%20central%20panel%20were%20conducted%20through%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20while%20voting%20for%20the%20college%20union%20polls%20was%20on%20paper%20ballots.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20students%2C%20core%20issues%20ranged%20from%20fee%20hikes%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20affordable%20accommodations%2C%20enhanced%20security%20during%20college%20fests%20and%20menstrual%20leaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ABVP%2C%20Congress-affiliated%20NSUI%2C%20CPI(M)-backed%20Students'%20Federation%20of%20India%20(SFI)%20and%20the%20CPI(ML)-Liberation-linked%20All%20India%20Students'%20Association%20(AISA)%20had%20fielded%20candidates%20for%20all%20four%20central%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20DUSU%20is%20the%20main%20representative%20body%20for%20most%20colleges%20and%20faculties.%20Each%20college%20also%20has%20its%20own%20students'%20union%2C%20elections%20to%20which%20are%20held%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20t