%20the%20bond%20the%20he%20witnessed%20the%20Kapoor%20clan%20sharing%20during%20the%20shoot%20of%20%3Cem%3EJaane%20Jaan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CSaif%20was%20there%20to%20babysit%20the%20kids%20when%20she%20was%20shooting%2C%20and%20very%20lovely%20to%20see%20the%20entire%20family.%20The%20little%20one%20was%20on%20the%20set%20holding%20a%20mic%20and%20trying%20to%20sing.%20So%2C%20it%20was%20a%20very%20beautiful%20environment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVijay%20Varma%2C%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20also%20spoke%20about%20working%20with%20the%20Kapoor%20sisters.%20The%20actor%20said%20that%20his%20experience%20%E2%80%9Chas%20been%20like%20a%20fairy%20tale.%E2%80%9D%20He%20told%20News18%2C%20%E2%80%9CKareena%20and%20Karisma%20have%20years%20of%20experience%20behind%20them%2C%20which%20is%20amazing.%20They%20know%20the%20business%20and%20the%20camera%20and%20they%20understand%20how%20to%20work%20around%20it%20so%20beautifully.%20It%20was%20delightful%20to%20just%20watch%20the%20both%20of%20them%20at%20work.%20I%20managed%20to%20have%20informal%2C%20off-camera%20moments%20with%20them%20which%20were%20very%20nice%20as%20well.%20I%20grew%20up%20watching%20and%20%3Cem%3Eseeti%20maaroing%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20both%20of%20their%20films%20and%20to%20work%20with%20them%20now%20has%20been%20like%20a%20fairy%20tale.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20NDTV%20Saibal%20Chatterjee%2C%20in%20his%20review%20of%20%3Cem%3EJaane%20Jaan%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewrote%2C%20%26quot%3BJaane%20Jaan%20explores%20the%20debilitating%20isolation%20of%20a%20man%20lost%20in%20his%20own%20world%20as%20well%20as%20the%20pitfalls%20in%20the%20way%20of%20a%20woman%20determined%20to%20put%20her%20troubled%20past%20behind%20her.%20Multiple%20dualities%20-%20protector-predator%2C%20victim-perpetrator%2C%20friend-foe%20and%20genius-oddball%20-%20are%20central%20to%20the%20twisted%20plot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20is%20based%20on%20the%20third%20novel%20of%20Keigo%20Higashino's%20Detective%20G