%20%E2%80%9Ccoordinating%E2%80%9D%20with%20Canada%20on%20this%20diplomatic%20fracas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBlinken%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20were%20further%20preceded%20by%20US%20national%20security%20advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20who%20observed%20that%20no%20country%20could%20get%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-killing-us-canada-no-special-exemption%5C%22%3Especial%20exemption%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20for%20such%20activities%2C%20like%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20Canada%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20government%20agents%20in%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing.%20Sullivan%20had%20also%20urged%20India%20to%20join%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20denied%20a%20%3Cem%3EWashington%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-killing-us-canada-no-special-exemption%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20had%20said%20that%20Canada%20had%20reached%20out%20to%20its%20closest%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20openly%20condemn%20the%20murder%20of%20its%20citizen%20weeks%20before%20Trudeau%20went%20public%20with%20allegations%20against%20India.%20%E2%80%9CVery%20bluntly%2C%20I%20will%20say%20that%20%E2%80%93%20and%20you%20know%20me%20well%20enough%20%E2%80%93%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20commenting%20on%20private%20diplomatic%20conversations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Cohen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20I%20will%20say%20this%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20shared%20intelligence%20information%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20communication%20between%20Canada%20and%20the%20United%20States%20about%20this%2C%20and%20I%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20as%20far%20as%20I%E2%80%99m%20comfortable%20going.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20if%20there%20is%20any%20hesitancy%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Joe%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20administration%20to%20side%20with%20Canada%20on%20the%20allegations%2C%20Coh