d%20asking%20why%20you%20are%20asking%20questions%20to%20the%20innocent%20instead%20of%20asking%20the%20person%20who%20should%20be%20guilty.%20Only%20a%20certain%20section%20of%20the%20people%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20they%20always%20play%20the%20victim%20card.%20But%20whenever%20there%20is%20something%20new%20happening%2C%20there%20will%20be%20some%20resistance%20to%20change%20by%20a%20few%20people%20and%20that%20is%20understandable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%20talking%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20Ashwin%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20I%20am%20talking%20about%20the%20run-out%20at%20the%20non-striker's%20end%20done%20by%20Deepti%20Sharma%20dismissing%20Charlie%20Dean.%20I%20have%20already%20spoken%20enough%20on%20this%20subject%20already.%20So%20let%20me%20be%20short%20and%20sweet%20today.%20Risk%20vs%20Reward.%20Just%20like%20how%20a%20batter%20knows%20when%20he%20steps%20out%20of%20the%20crease%20against%20a%20spinner%20or%20a%20pacer%20that%20a%20wicketkeeper%20can%20dismiss%20them%20by%20stumping.%20Likewise%2C%20a%20non-striker%20should%20also%20know%20that%20he%20can%20be%20dismissed%20run-out%20legitimately%20if%20they%20keep%20stepping%20out%20of%20the%20crease%20and%20taking%20that%20extra%20yard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20teach%20the%20kids%20right%20from%20when%20they%20are%20young%20on%20this.%20Because%20in%20today's%20world%20of%20competitive%20cricket%2C%20I%20spoke%20about%20this%20during%20the%20Ahmedabad%20Test%20match%20when%20the%20pitch%20issue'%20was%20brought%20up%20on%20what%20was%20a%20good%20pitch.%20I%20told%20'do%20not%20control%20the%20narratives'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBecause%20a%20certain%20section%20of%20people%20consciously%20chooses%20to%20instill%20in%20others%20how%20they%20should%20think%20about%20a%20certain%20thing.%20They%20control%20their%20narratives.%20There%20are%20many%20articles%20on%20this%20exact%20subject.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20see%20this%20as%20a%20bowler's%20revolution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695477180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvhdslge8_ish-sodhi-run-out_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fish-sodhi-run-out-by-bangladesh-star-at-non-strikers-end-still-stays-on-not-out-heres-how-watch-4417493%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20cricket%2C%20the%20run%20out%20at%20the%20non-striker's%20end%20is%20currently%20legal%2C%20but%20still%20contentious.%20Every%20time%20any%20attempt%20to%20run%20out%20a%20player%20at%20the%20non-striker's%20end%20happens%2C%20there%20is%20controversy%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fish-sodhi-run-out-by-bangladesh-star-at-non-strikers-end-still-stays-on-not-out-heres-how-watch-4417493%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fish-sodhi-run-out-by-bangladesh-star-at-non-strikers-end-still-stays-on-not-out-heres-how-watch-4417493%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fish-sodhi-run-out-by-bangladesh-star-at-non-strikers-end-still-stays-on-not-out-heres-how-watch-4417493%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20In%20Udaipur%20For%20Parineeti-Raghav%20Wedding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20his%20Punjab%20counterpart%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20landed%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Udaipur%20today%20ahead%20of%20the%20wedding%20of%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20and%20actor%20Parineeti%20Chopra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20politicians%20and%20film%20personalities%20will%20attend%20the%20pre-wedding%20events%20today%20and%20the%20main%20ceremony%20tomorrow%20at%20The%20Leela%20Palace.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParineet