20the%20name%20of%20journalism%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20press%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20clear%20yet%20which%20%E2%80%9Cfake%20reports%E2%80%9D%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20is%20referring%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20finance%20minister%2C%20Ibrahim%20Ameer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.sun.mv%2F84837%5C%22%3Ehas%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20are%20reports%20being%20circulated%20stating%20that%20he%20had%20met%20with%20the%20Indian%20high%20commissioner%20in%20the%20Maldives%20to%20seek%20a%20loan%20of%20MVR%203%20billion%20from%20the%20Indian%20government.%20Ameer%20categorically%20denied%20that%20there%20were%20any%20such%20meetings%20and%20any%20such%20request%20made%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20by%20the%20Maldivian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20Maldives%20have%20been%20critical%20of%20President%20Ibrahim%20Solih%E2%80%99s%20engagement%20with%20India.%20He%20has%20come%20under%20fierce%20attack%20from%20the%20opposition%20camp%20for%20letting%20India%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Findia-ibrahim-solih-maldives-presidential-election%5C%22%3Edictate%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20the%20policies%20of%20his%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20principal%20opposition%20coalition%20of%20the%20Progressive%20Party%20of%20Maldives%20(PPM)%20and%20the%20Progressive%20National%20Congress%20(PNC)%20has%20spearheaded%20an%20%E2%80%98India%20Out%E2%80%99%20campaign%20on%20the%20alleged%20grounds%20that%20Solih%20had%20allowed%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20to%20be%20stationed%20in%20Maldives.%20Both%20Mal%C3%A9%20and%20New%20Delhi%20have%20denied%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20September%209%2C%20Maldives%20held%20its%20fourth%20multi-party%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmaldives-polls-solih-india-mohamed-muizzu-china%5C%22%3E%20presidential%20election%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20largest%20pool%20of%20candidates.%20President%20Solih%2C%20who%20is%20seen%20as%20favourable%20to%20India%2C%20secured%20a%20distant%20second-place%20position%20against%20PPM-PNC%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20backed%20by%20China.%20While%20Muizzu%20secured%2046%25%20votes%2C%20Solih%20managed%20to%20win%2039%25%20of%20the%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Maldivian%20electoral%20system%2C%20a%20second%20round%20of%20voting%20is%20necessary%20if%20no%20candidate%20bags%20at%20least%2050%25%20of%20votes.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Solih%20and%20Muizzu%20will%20face%20off%20in%20the%20second%20round%20on%20September%2030.%20Going%20by%20trends%2C%20it%20appears%20Solih%E2%80%99s%20dreams%20of%20winning%20re-election%20may%20not%20be%20successful%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20major%20criticisms%20against%20his%20government%20has%20been%20that%20he%20has%20allowed%20New%20Delhi%20to%20dictate%20his%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20principal%20driver%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98India%20Out%E2%80%99%20campaign%20had%20been%20former%20President%20Abdulla%20Yameen.%20But%20since%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20refused%20to%20accept%20his%20appeal%20to%20stand%20for%20election%20despite%20his%20conviction%2C%20the%20opposition%20coalition%20brought%20in%20former%20housing%20minister%20Miuzzi%2C%20who%20has%20carried%20forward%20the%20same%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20presidential%20debate%2C%20Solih%20was%20attacked%20on%20his%20alleged%20approval%20for%20Indian%20troops%20being%20stationed%20in%20the%20Maldives.%20This%20allegation%20had%20also%20been%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98India%20Out%E2%80%99%20campaign%20that%20had%20been%20spearheaded%20by%20former%20President%20Abdulla%20Yameen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20President%20Solih%20and%20his%20government%20denied%20those%20allegations%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20perception%20that%20his%20government%20has%20been%20batting%20from%20the%20backfoot%20while%20facing%20the%20relentless%20allegations.%C2%A0The%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20Maldives%20had%20to%20also%20issue%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FHCIMaldives%2Fstatus%2F1701824377015411140%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Etwo%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FHCIMaldives%2Fstatus%2F1699691510424609095%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Efact-checks%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20opposition%20supporters%20circulated%20false%20documents%20claiming%20Indian%20military%20presence%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20nation.%C2%A0For%20India%2C%20an%20electoral%20loss%20for%20Solih%20would%20be%20a%20big%20setback.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695465926000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F08%2F29223756%2FScreen-Shot-2020-08-29-at-10.37.21-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-condemns-fake-reports-in-maldivian-press-to-harass-high-commission-staff-diaspora%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20Maldives%20head%20for%20a%20run-off%20vote%20in%20the%20presidential%20election%20on%20September%2030%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20been%20banking%20on%20its%20'India%20Out'%20campaign%2C%20accusing%20President%20Ibrahim%20Solih%20of%20allowing%20India%20to%20'dictate'%20his%20government's%20policies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-condemns-fake-reports-in-maldivian-press-to-harass-high-commission-staff-diaspora%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20Has%20Exposed%20the%20Real%20Face%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Beyond%20PR%20Charm%20Offensives%2C%20Studied%20Silences%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F23131246%2FThe-Wire-17.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MP%20from%20South%20Delhi%2C%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-ramesh-bidhuri-targets-fellow-mp-with-religious-slurs-provokes-outrage-101695375926543.html%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20fellow%20MP%2C%20Danish%20Ali%2C%20%E2%80%98pimp%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98terrorist%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98militant%E2%80%99%20and%20also%20used%20the%20words%20%3Cem%3Emullah%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekatwa%20%E2%80%93%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0a%20pejorative%20word%20for%20a%20Muslim%20who%20is%20circumcised.%20The%20abuse%20was%20hurled%20across%20the%20floor%20of%20parliament.%20Bidhuri%20also%20demanded%20that%20Ali%20be%20thrown%20out%20of%20parliament.%20Sitting%20next%20to%20Bidhuri%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fharsh-vardhan-ramesh-bidhuri-remark-8951328%2F%5C%22%3Etwo%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Harsh%20Vardhan%2C%20former%20minister%20of%20health%20and%20also%20science%20and%20technology%2C%20and%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%2C%20former%20minister%20of%20law%20and%20justice%20and%20communications%20and%20information%20technology.%20Both%20of%20these%20senior%20members%20of%20the%20BJP%20were%20laughing%20throughout%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20rant.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20speaker%20of%20parliament%2C%20Om%20Prakash%20Birla%2C%20warned%20Bidhuri%20that%20such%20behaviour%20would%20lead%20to%20penalties%20in%20the%20future%20and%20he%20also%20expunged%20the%20abusive%20comments.%20The%20BJP%20has%20issued%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%20to%20Bidhuri%20but%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20any%20action%20will%20be%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20outrage%20against%20this%20incident%20has%20come%20from%20the%20opposition%20but%20also%20from%20those%20who%20are%20sympathetic%20to%20the%20BJP.%20The%20latter%20seems%20more%20upset%20that%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20newly%20built%20parliament%20was%20violated%20rather%20than%20caring%20about%20the%20insults%20and%20tenor%20of%20the%20language.%20However%2C%20it%20should%20not%20be%20surprising%20that%20the%20provocative%2C%20virulent%20and%20prejudiced%20language%20used%20in%20public%20rallies%20by%20some%20BJP%20leaders%20has%20found%20its%20way%20into%20parliament.%20Of%20course%2C%20it%20is%20easier%20to%20dismiss%20public%20speeches%20as%20anomalous%20and%20rather%20more%20difficult%20to%20ignore%20what%20is%20said%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuri-is-simply-the-means-the-real-end-is-to-cause-despair%5C%22%3ERamesh%20Bidhuri%20Is%20Simply%20the%20Means%2C%20the%20Real%20End%20Is%20to%20Cause%20Despair%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20Muslims%20can%20be%20called%20traitors%20and%20likened%20to%20pathogens%2C%20diseases%20and%20insects%20in%20public%20speeches%20by%20BJP%20MPs%20then%20why%20use%20the%20fig%20leaf%20of%20parliamentary%20procedure%20to%20pretend%20as%20if%20politics%20in%20India%20still%20adheres%20to%20some%20imaginary%20standard%20of%20public%20engagement%3F%20Why%20outrage%20at%20what%20Bidhuri%20said%20in%20parliament%20when%20this%20is%20precisely%20the%20language%20used%20in%20WhatsApp%20groups%2C%20local%20meetings%2C%20public%20rallies%20and%20occasionally%20on%20television%20by%20both%20BJP%20members%20and%20its%20supporters%3F%20What%20Bidhuri%20has%20done%20has%20inadvertently%20drawn%20attention%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20lowest%20common%20denominator%20that%20binds%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20politics%20is%20the%20spectre%20of%20the%20Muslim%20as%20the%20sub-human%20other%2C%20the%20perennial%20enemy%2C%20the%20cancer%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20body%20politic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20BJP%20realised%20that%20the%20exigencies%20of%20power%20meant%20that%20such%20odious%20views%20must%20be%20suitably%20camouflaged%20if%20not%20hidden%20entirely.%20So%2C%20with%20some%20help%20from%20spin%20doctors%2C%20the%20party%20mastered%20the%20art%20of%20speaking%20in%20tongues.%20This%20approach%20allows%20plausible%20deniability%20and%20also%20placates%20the%20conscience%20of%20those%20who%20support%20the%20BJP%20and%20believe%20that%20these%20bigoted%20voices%20are%20peripheral%2C%20radical%20and%20do%20not%20represent%20the%20party.%20If%20a%20party%20apparatchik%20or%20even%20leader%20does%20say%20something%20that%20causes%20too%20much%20outrage%2C%20then%20there%20is%20a%20light%20tap%20on%20the%20wrist%20or%20a%20studied%20silence%2C%20depending%20on%20what%20the%20wider%20fallout%20is.%20Often%2C%20international%20coverage%20of%20hate%20speech%20or%20incidents%20of%20communal%20violence%20catalyses%20some%20kind%20of%20anodyne%20response%20about%20how%20all%20Indians%20are%20equal%20and%20how%20the%20BJP%20works%20night%20and%20day%20for%20the%20good%20of%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20can%E2%80%99t%20unlink%20itself%20from%20divisiveness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20in%20July%20this%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20actually%20sought%20to%20change%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20perception%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20Muslims.%20He%20asked%20BJP%20workers%20to%20take%20out%20%E2%80%98Sneh%20Yatras%E2%80%99%20or%20goodwill%20processions%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20Pasmanda%20Muslims.%20This%20referred%20to%20the%20most%20marginalised%2C%20oppressed%20and%20economically%20backward%20members%20of%20the%20community%20who%20are%20distinct%20from%20%E2%80%98upper-caste%E2%80%99%20Ashraf%20Muslims.%20Ironically%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%20who%20are%20the%20biggest%20victims%20of%20mob%20lynching%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20communal%20violence.%20True%20to%20its%20word%2C%20the%20BJP%20actually%20fielded%20390%20odd%20Muslim%20candidates%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20municipal%20elections%20this%20year.%20This%20move%20was%20widely%20hailed%20as%20a%20pathbreaking%20moment%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20BJP%20as%20the%20leadership%20claimed%20they%20wanted%20to%20now%20provide%20representation%20for%20Muslims%20within%20the%20party%20eve