lash%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20Ravi%20Shankar%20Prasad%20would%20care%20to%20explain%20whether%20what%20he%20witnessed%20in%20parliament%20and%20his%20laughter%20were%20examples%20of%20the%20positive%20politics%20he%20spoke%20of%20earlier%20this%20year.%20While%20many%20people%20have%20called%20for%20action%20against%20Bidhuri%2C%20it%20would%20be%20worthwhile%20remembering%20that%20he%20is%20merely%20a%20symptom%20of%20a%20much%20larger%20malaise.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20his%20actions%20should%20sound%20the%20warning%20bells%20to%20those%20Muslims%20who%20genuinely%20believe%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20making%20space%20for%20them.%20Even%20if%20the%20argument%20is%20made%20that%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20views%20are%20peripheral%20or%20not%20representative%20then%20what%20will%20ultimately%20matter%20is%20what%20action%20is%20taken%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDefence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20issued%20a%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmassive-outrage-speakers-warning-over-bjp-mp-ramesh-bidhuris-offensive-comments-4413477%5C%22%3Esaying%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CI%20express%20regret%20if%20the%20opposition%20is%20hurt%20by%20the%20remarks%20made%20by%20the%20member.%E2%80%9D%20The%20very%20fact%20that%20he%20%E2%80%98expressed%20regret%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20opposition%20and%20did%20not%20acknowledge%20or%20apologise%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20slurs%20implicitly%20targeted%20an%20entire%20community%20speaks%20volumes%20about%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20fundamentally%20distance%20itself%20from%20a%20politics%20that%20is%20built%20on%20divisive%20foundations.%20Rajnath%20Singh%20is%20known%20to%20keep%20good%20relations%20with%20many%20senior%20Muslim%20leaders%20but%20even%20he%20had%20to%20give%20a%20very%20carefully%20worded%20statement%20in%20case%20of%20backlash%20from%20BJP%20supporters.%20Ultimately%2C%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20outburst%20briefly%20%E2