5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20government%20may%20remove%20the%20requirement%20for%20a%20mandatory%20licence%20to%20import%20laptops%2C%20personal%20computers%2C%20and%20tablets.%20Instead%2C%20companies%20may%20only%20need%20to%20register%20on%20a%20portal%20to%20import%20these%20items%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2F2023%2Fsep%2F23%2Flaptop-pc-import-licencing-may-go-2617512.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20quoting%20industry%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20suggested%20the%20possibility%20of%20providing%20a%20one-year%20grace%20period%20for%20importing%20these%20products%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20daily%20quoted%20industry%20sources%20as%20saying%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cimport%20management%20system%E2%80%9D%20portal%2C%20which%20will%20be%20managed%20by%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%20(DGFT)%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20go%20live%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20sudden%20import%20ban%20on%20these%20items.%20However%2C%20the%20government%20indicated%20that%20it%20may%20extend%20the%20deadline%20by%20another%20year.%20Now%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20seek%20any%20licences%20but%20only%20need%20to%20register.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20companies%20can%20import%20as%20much%20quantity%20as%20they%20want%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20source%20told%20the%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20had%20on%20August%203%20banned%20imports%20of%20personal%20computers%20without%20a%20license%20with%20immediate%20effect.%20The%20move%20was%20aimed%20at%20preventing%20Chinese%20imports%20from%20flooding%20Indian%20markets%20and%20to%20promote%20local%20manufacturing.%20However%2C%20while%20taking%20this%20decision%2C%20it%20seemed%20to%20have%20not%20considered%20that%2080%25%20of%20the%20devices%20sold%20in%20India%20are%20imported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20day%2C%20it%20clarified%20that%20there%20was%20no%20ban%2C%20but%20electronic%20manufacturing%20companies%20needed%20a%20licence%20to%20import%20these%20items%20starting%20from%20November%201%2C%202023.%20The%20Minister%20of%20State%2C%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20again%20clarified%20that%20it%20was%20not%20licencing%20but%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-a-face-saving-move-centre-mulls-lifting-curbs-on-import-of-personal-computers%5C%22%3Eimport%20management%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20be%20put%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20accept%20that%20there%20was%20a%20communication%20gap%3B%20it%20was%20never%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20licencing%20requirement.%20Today%2C%20we%20are%20meeting%20with%20industry%20representatives%20and%20sharing%20a%20draft%20of%20the%20import%20management%20system.%20Its%20aim%20is%20to%20address%20the%20high%20dependency%20on%20sources%20that%20are%20not%20verified%20and%20trusted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chandrasekhar%20told%20the%20newspaper%20on%20September%2023%2C%20at%20the%20ceremony%20for%20Micron%20Technology%E2%80%99s%20semiconductor%20testing%20and%20assembly%20plant%20in%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20Sanand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20credit-based%20system%2C%20manufacturers%20will%20be%20assessed%20on%20three%20criteria%3A%20their%20past%20year%E2%80%99s%20imports%2C%20progress%20on%20domestic%20manufacturing%20of%20IT%20hardware%20products%2C%20and%20exports%20from%20India.%20Based%20on%20their%20performance%20on%20these%20parameters%20the%20government%20will%20allot%20them%20credit%20points%20which%20can%20be%20used%20to%20import%20laptops%20and%20other%20IT%20hardware%20products%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fbusiness%2Findustry-relief-for-apple-samsung-credit-system-to-replace-import-licensing-3252269%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20explained%20the%20process%20with%20the%20help%20of%20an%20example.%20%E2%80%9CApple%20and%20Samsung%20have%20not%20applied%20for%20the%20production-linked%20incentive%20scheme%20for%20IT%20hardware%20for%20domestic%20manufacturing%20but%20are%20making%20mobile%20phones%20in%20the%20country%20under%20the%20smartphone%20PLI%20and%20are%20exporting%20in%20huge%20numbers.%20The%20credit%20points%20which%20will%20accrue%20to%20them%20due%20to%20this%20will%20ensure%20that%20their%20import%20continues%20smoothly%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695462423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F13173221%2Fglenn-carstens-peters-npxXWgQ33ZQ-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovt-may-remove-the-requirement-for-mandatory-licence-to-import-laptops-pcs-tablets-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20also%20suggested%20the%20possibility%20of%20providing%20a%20one-year%20grace%20period%20for%20importing%20these%20products.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovt-may-remove-the-requirement-for-mandatory-licence-to-import-laptops-pcs-tablets-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Divorce%20Drama%20%E2%80%98Lovable%E2%80%99%20Asks%20What%20It%20Means%20to%20Be%20a%20%E2%80%98Strong%2C%20Modern%20Woman%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20Face%20of%20a%20Messy%20Break-Up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695461569000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FLovable.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235733247%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Norway%E2%80%99s%20Lilja%20Ingolfsdottir%20won%20the%20top%20prize%20this%20week%20at%20the%20Finnish%20Film%20Affair%20for%20her%20feature%20directo