%20in%20the%20Old%20Testament%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20spirit%20of%20a%20man%20sustains%20him%2C%20but%20a%20wounded%20spirit%20who%20can%20bear%3F%E2%80%9D%20(Proverbs%2014%3A18)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBidhuri%E2%80%99s%20words%20were%20designed%20to%20wound%2C%20and%20they%20did.%20They%20shocked%20and%20stunned%20not%20just%20the%20recipient%20but%20many%20others.%20Undoubtedly%2C%20they%20reopened%20old%20and%20not-so-old%20wounds%20in%20the%20minds%20of%20many%20Indian%20Muslims%20who%20have%20been%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20slurs%20like%20the%20ones%20Ali%20was.%20Not%20just%20Muslims%2C%20anyone%20with%20a%20modicum%20of%20decency%20and%20empathy%20would%20have%20felt%20outraged%2C%20possibly%20even%20despondent%2C%20at%20how%20low%20public%20discourse%20has%20fallen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fwide-range-of-fears-new-indias-muslims-have%5C%22%3EHow%20Are%20India%E2%80%99s%20Muslims%20Feeling%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20me%20personally%2C%20the%20incident%20brought%20back%20to%20mind%20an%20event%20that%20transpired%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20Driving%20down%20South%20Delhi%20(Ramesh%20Bidhuri%E2%80%99s%20constituency)%20with%20a%20friend%20one%20late%20Friday%20afternoon%2C%20we%20passed%20a%20group%20of%20Muslims%20in%20skull%20caps%20who%20had%20probably%20just%20finished%20offering%20their%20%3Cem%3Enamaz%3C%2Fem%3E.%20My%20friend%20said%20with%20a%20clear%20note%20of%20scorn%20in%20her%20voice%2C%20%E2%80%9COh%20look%2C%20there%20go%20your%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20you%20mean%3F%E2%80%9D%20I%20said%2C%20genuinely%20mystified.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20%3Cem%3Emullahs%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20your%20favourite%20people%2C%20aren%E2%80%99t%20they%3F%20You%20are%20always%20standing%20up%20for%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20atmosphere%20in%20the%20car%20became%20tense.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlease%20don%E