0down.%20There%20is%20no%20word%20yet%20on%20a%20potential%20deal%2C%20but%20insiders%20with%20knowledge%20of%20ongoings%20in%20the%20room%20say%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fwga-amptp-talks-still-going-friday-night-1235733166%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fwga-amptp-talks-still-going-friday-night-1235733166%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fwga-amptp-talks-still-going-friday-night-1235733166%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aboard%20the%20Karmabhumi%20Express%2C%20a%20Reporter%20Learns%20of%20the%20Dreams%20of%20Bengal's%20Outbound%20Migrants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22171027%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-5.09.51.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarmabhumi%20Express%20(West%20Bengal)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Welcome%20aboard%20the%2022512%20Kamakhya-LTT%20Karmabhumi%20Express%20%E2%80%93%20a%20metaphor%2C%20if%20any%2C%20of%20the%20acuteness%20of%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20unemployment%20problem.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%2010.28%20pm%20at%20north%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Alipurduar%20Junction%20and%20the%20crowd%20has%20swollen%20to%20its%20peak.%20This%20is%20when%20the%20%3Cspan%3EKarmabhumi%20Express%20appears%20at%20the%20station.%20It%20is%20bound%20for%20Mumbai.%20Finding%20a%20seat%20on%20it%20is%20close%20to%20impossible.%20It%20is%20always%20chock%20full%20and%20there%20are%20always%20hundreds%20struggling%20to%20get%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20unreserved%20general%20compartment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20railway%20reservation%20official%20is%20looking%20at%20the%20crowd.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20working%20on%20this%20route%20since%202015%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20always%20been%20an%20extraordinary%20scene%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20a%20well%20known%20fact%20that%20the%20seats%20on%20this%20train%20get%20snapped%20up%20%E2%80%93%20the%20official%20says%20even%20four%20months%20%E2%80%93%20ahead%20of%20time.%20%E2%80%9CYoung%20people%20from%20lower-middle%20class%20backgrounds%20board%20this%20train%20in%20search%20of%20a%20livelihood.%20They%20are%20even%20willing%20to%20pay%20extra%20for%20AC%20tickets%20if%20sleeper%20class%20reservations%20aren%E2%80%99t%20available%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20train%2C%20originally%20introduced%20in%20the%202010%20Railway%20Budget%20by%20then%20Union%20railway%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20was%20initially%20intended%20to%20run%20as%20an%20unreserved%20service%20catering%20to%20migrant%20workers.%20Now%2C%20Banerjee%20is%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bengal%2C%20which%20has%20seen%20a%20crippling%20lack%20of%20jobs%20for%20its%20young.%20However%2C%20out%20of%20the%2020%20compartments%2C%20only%20three%20remain%20designated%20as%20unreserved.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20stepped%20onto%20the%20train%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20to%20me%20that%20there%20were%20going%20to%20be%20no%20seats%20available%20for%20me.%20I%20simply%20followed%20the%20example%20of%20my%20fellow%20passengers%20and%20settled%20down%20on%20the%20floor%2C%20using%20an%20old%20newspaper%20as%20cushion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20train%20is%20commonly%20recognised%20as%20the%20lifeline%20connecting%20the%20northeastern%20and%20eastern%20states%20of%20Assam%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Odisha%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20financial%20hub.%20It%20takes%20approximately%2054%20hours%20to%20make%20the%20entire%20journey%20and%20almost%20invariably%20operates%20beyond%20its%20designated%20capacity.%20On%20the%20day%20I%20travelled%2C%20there%20were%20nearly%20500%20passengers%20on%20the%20general%20compartment%20meant%20for%20120.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%E2%80%99re%20getting%20off%20at%20Burdwan%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99m%20headed%20all%20the%20way%20to%20Mumbai.%20You%E2%80%99ll%20reach%20by%20tomorrow%20noon%2C%20whereas%20I%E2%80%99ll%20be%20getting%20off%20three%20days%20from%20now.%20Just%20wait%20and%20see%20the%20size%20of%20the%20crowd%2C%20it%E2%80%99ll%20grow!%E2%80%9D%20says%20my%20co-passenger%20Arup%20Deka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeka%20was%20right.%20At%20every%20station%20along%20the%20way%2C%20more%20passengers%20continued%20to%20board%20the%20compartment%2C%20gradually%20filling%20even%20the%20spaces%20intended%20for%20luggage%20and%20those%20outside%20the%20restrooms.%20Many%20of%20the%20passengers%20carried%20bulky%20luggage%2C%20including%20bedding.%20From%20my%20conversations%20with%20them%2C%20it%20became%20apparent%20that%20almost%20everyone%20on%20this%20journey%20was%20migrating%20in%20search%20of%20better%20opportunities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESwapan%20Dutta%2C%20seated%20in%20front%20of%20me%2C%20has%20been%20working%20in%20Mumbai%20for%20many%20years%2C%20similar%20to%20many%20of%20my%20middle-aged%20co-passengers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESwapan%20says%20that%20every%20time%20he%20returns%20to%20his%20village%2C%20people%20ask%20him%20to%20help%20their%20sons%20find%20work%20in%20other%20states.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20young%20men%20are%20sitting%20idle%20at%20home%20because%20there%20are%20no%20job%20opportunities%20in%20the%20villages.%20We%20assist%20the%20youth%20from%20our%20villages%20in%20moving%20to%20places%20where%20jobs%20are%20available.%20They%20gradually%20learn%20the%20skills%20of%20the%20trade%2C%20start%20earning%2C%20and%20become%20confident%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20all%2C%20families%20cannot%20marry%20off%20their%20sons%20just%20to%20ease%20their%20financial%20burdens%2C%E2%80%9D%20indicating%20that%20this%20is%20common%20practice%20for%20daughters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTell%20me%2C%20where%20can%20they%20find%20work%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%20Swapan%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22170758%2FIMG_2658-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22170758%2FIMG_2658-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22170758%2FIMG_2658-1-300x187.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22170758%2FIMG_2658-1-1024x639.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674380%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22749%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20continuous%20rise%20in%20movement%20from%20West%20Bengal%20to%20other%20states%20in%20search%20of%20a%20livelihood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2021%2F29%2Fcommentary%2Fmigrant-workers-west-bengal-1991.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20study%20published%20by%20Avijit%20Mistry%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20and%20Political%20Weekly%3C%2Fem%3E%20%20in%202021%20revealed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20during%20the%202010s%2C%20there%20was%20a%20net%20outflow%20of%20people%20from%20the%20state%2C%20surpassing%20the%20number%20of%20individuals%20who%20moved%20in.%20While%20the%20initial%20signs%20of%20this%20crisis%20emerged%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20Left%20Front%20government%E2%80%99s%20rule%2C%20the%20situation%20has%20deteriorated%20further%20under%20the%20current%20regime.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBetween%202001%20to%202011%2C%20one%20lakh%20people%20had%20migrated%20out%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20but%20in%20the%20following%20eight%20years%2C%20the%20number%20skyrocketed%20to%2011%20lakhs.%20A%20significant%20portion%20of%20these%20migrants%20are%20seasonal%20labourers%20seeking%20better%20job%20prospects%2C%20particularly%20in%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20the%20southern%20regions%2C%20which%20offer%20considerably%20higher%20wages%20than%20West%20Bengal%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20economist%20Ratan%20Khasnabish.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20state%20government%20has%20not%20officially%20released%20data%20on%20inter-state%20migration%2C%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20lockdown%2C%20CM%20Banerjee%20announced%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20bring%20back%2010.5%20lakh%20people%20from%20various%20regions%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20Migrant%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Union%20(WBMWU)%2C%20which%20is%20affiliated%20with%20CITU%2C%20the%20labour%20wing%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%2C%20has%20carried%20out%20an%20initial%20statewide%20survey%20which%20has%20identified%20over%2060%20lakh%20individuals%20who%20have%20migrated%20to%20other%20states.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20villages%20in%20West%20Bengal%20where%20the%20entire%20adult%20male%20population%20has%20migrated%20to%20other%20states%20for%20work.%20This%20is%20unprecedented%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Asadullah%20Gayen%2C%20a%20functionary%20of%20the%20WBMWU.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGayen%20feels%20that%20the%20numbers%20at%20which%20Bengal%20youth%20migrate%20away%20also%20makes%20them%20vulnerable%20to%20anger%20from%20the%20original%20population%20of%20youths%20in%20other%20states%2C%20who%20feel%20that%20their%20local%20jobs%20are%20being%20taken%20away%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22170746%2FIMG_2660-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22170746%2FIMG_2660-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22170746%2FIMG_2660-1-300x187.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22170746%2FIMG_2660-1-1024x639.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674379%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22749%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20train%2C%20Sagar%20Mandal%20from%20the%20same%20Alipurduar%20district%20says%20he%20was%20forced%20leave%20his%20village%20near%20Hasimara%20in%20search%20of%20a%20job.%20His%20family%20had%20worked%20in%20the%20local%20tea%20gardens%20for%20generations%2C%20but%20the%20low%20wages%20in%20the%20tea%20industry%20made%20it%20increasingly%20challenging%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMandal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20in%20my%20family%2C%20including%20my%20grandfather%20is%20employed%20in%20the%20tea%20garden%2C%20but%20our%20daily%20earnings%20hardly%20reach%20Rs%20600.%20I%20used%20to%20work%20as%20a%20daily%20labourer%20for%20a%20boulder%20contractor%2C%20but%20the%20pay%20was%20inconsistent.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20work%20every%20day.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20Maqbool%2C%20a%20job%20contractor%20in%20Mumbai.%20He%E2%80%99s%20suggested%20that%20I%20relocate%20there%20for%20better%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20travellers%20on%20the%20train%20who%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20job%20had%20depended%20on%20either%20neighbours%20or%20relatives%20who%20already%20had%20one%20or%20labour%20contractors%2C%20like%20Mandal%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20overhear%20a%20passenger%20talking%20to%20his%20mother%20on%20his%20phone.%20%E2%80%9CGo%20to%20sleep%2C%20ma.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20worry.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20be%20there%20soon.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20broker%20there%20who%20said%20he%E2%80%99ll%20find%20a%20job%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20journey%20continues%2C%20some%20passengers%20doze%20off%2C%20while%20others%20turn%20to%20their%20phones%20for%20entertainment.%20In%20one%20corner%2C%20a%20boy%20begins%20to%20cry.%20Hearing%20his%20sobs%2C%20a%20fellow%20passenger%20in%20his%20twenties%20comes%20down%20from%20the%20bunk%20and%20puts%20an%20arm%20around%20him.%20%E2%80%9CCome%20with%20me%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebhai%3C%2Fem%3E.%20We%E2%80%99ll%20work%20there%2C%20and%20everything%20will%20get%20better.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20working%20there%20for%20seven%20years%20now%2C%20and%20I%20too%20cried%20when%20I%20first%20took%20this%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20lines%20are%20laden%20with%20hope%20but%20they%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20true.%20Safety%2C%20in%20many%20of%20the%20industries%20where%20migrant%20youths%20work%20in%2C%20is%20an%20often%20neglected%20aspect.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMithu%20Bhoumik%2C%20a%20construction%20worker%20from%20North%20Dinajpur%2C%20says%20it%20is%20determination%20that%20keeps%20them%20going.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20newcomers%20learn%20by%20sheer%20determination.%20Do%20you%20think%20they%E2%80%99ll%20just%20stand%20around%20while%20everyone%20else%20works%3F%20They%E2%80%99ll%20start%20as%20helpers%20and%20will%20learn%20the%20tricks.%20I%20spent%20three%20months%20working%20with%20the%20head%20mason.%20I%20tied%20a%20rope%20around%20my%20waist%20and%20worked%20on%20the%20fifteenth%20floor%2C%20wiping%20and%20painting%20the%20glass%20windows%20from%20the%20outside.%20It%20made%20my%20head%20spin%20when%20I%20looked%20down%20at%20first%2C%20but%20I%20got%20used%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhowmik%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22170818%2FIMG_2661.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22170818%2FIMG_2661.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22170818%2FIMG_2661-300x187.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22170818%2FIMG_2661-1024x639.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674381%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22749%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20last%20month%2C%2023%20workers%20from%20the%20state%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20a%20tragic%20incident%20when%20an%20under-construction%20railway%20bridge%20collapsed%20in%20Mizoram%E2%80%99s%20Aizawl%20district.%20All%20of%20them%20were%20from%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Malda.%20Last%20week%2C%20a%20family%20of%20four%20from%20Alipurduar%20tragically%20suffocated%20to%20death%20in%20their%20small%20shack%20in%20Bengaluru.%20They%20had%20moved%20to%20the%20southern%20city%20only%2010%20days%20earlier%20to%20work%20in%20a%20poultry%20farm.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20earlier%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fcoromandel-express-bengal-migrants-labour-problem%5C%22%3E%20the%20June%202023%20derailment%20of%20the%20Coromandel%20Express%20laid%20bare%20the%20bitter%20truth%20of%20labourers%3C%2Fa%3E%20migrating%20to%20southern%20and%20western%20states%20in%20large%20numbers%20amid%20the%20drying%20up%20of%20central%20funds%20in%20the%20MGNREGA%20job%20guarantee%20scheme%20and%20the%20absence%20of%20rural%20jobs%20in%20the%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20state%20government%20formed%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Migrant%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Welfare%20Board%20to%20identify%20potential%20migrant%20labourers%20and%20create%20incentives%20for%20them%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20state%20as%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20plan%20to%20reduce%20the%20out-migration%20of%20low-skill%20or%20semi-skilled%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESamirual%20Islam%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20board%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20brushed%20away%20the%20suggestion%20that%20this%20was%20an%20issue%20plaguing%20Bengal%20particularly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fcoromandel-express-bengal-migrants-labour-problem%5C%22%3EA%20%E2%80%98Migrant%20Train%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20Coromandel%20Express%20Had%20Been%20the%20Ticket%20to%20a%20Livelihood%20for%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Poorest%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20migrant%20worker%20is%20not%20a%20Bengal-specific%20issue%2C%20other%20states%20are%20also%20facing%20this.%20The%20West%20Bengal%20government%20has%20launched%20an%20app%20for%20the%20migrant%20worker%2C%20the%20only%20state%20to%20do%20so.%20Duare%20Sarkar%2C%20the%20flagship%20outreach%20program%20of%20the%20government%20will%20focus%20on%20the%20registration%20of%20migrant%20workers.%20Please%20note%20that%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20labourers%20from%20states%20like%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20come%20to%20this%20state%20for%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Islam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20recent%20RBI%20study%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2Fkarnataka-in-5th-place-in-terms-of-corporate-investments-as-per-rbi-data%2Farticle67223175.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWest%20Bengal%20accounted%20for%20only%201%25%20of%20the%20total%20bank-assisted%20investment%20proposals%20made%20during%20the%20year%202022-23%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20total%20invested%20capital%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frbidocs.rbi.org.in%2Frdocs%2FPublications%2FPDFs%2F114T_1911202237AD8EFAF1664F87B9086E2C42102F93.PDF%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERs%208.38%20lakh%20crore%20between%20FY2016%20and%20FY2020%20in%20West%20Bengal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20significantly%20lower%20than%20Gujarat%20(Rs%2042.49%20lakh%20crore)%2C%20Maharashtra%20(Rs%2028.18%20lakh%20crore)%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20(Rs%2020.29%20lakh%20crore)%2C%20Odisha%20(Rs%2017.62%20lakh%20crore)%2C%20or%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20(Rs%2012.19%20lakh%20crore).%20The%20state%20also%20has%20fewer%20number%20factories%2C%20considering%20its%20high%20population%20density.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20co-passengers%20had%20varying%20levels%20of%20education%20and%20many%20had%20graduated%20school%20and%20college.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20Bijay%20Roy%20says%20he%20realised%20soon%20after%20finishing%20his%20Bachelor%20of%20Commerce%20that%20jobs%20were%20few.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLocal%20political%20leaders%20were%20selling%20government%20jobs%20for%20exorbitant%20sums%2C%20which%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20reach%20out%20directly%20to%20a%20contractor.%20Now%2C%20I%20work%20two%20jobs%20%E2%80%93%20a%20full-time%20one%20and%20a%20night%20shift%20as%20a%20technician.%20I%20earn%20around%20Rs%2040%2C000%20a%20month%20and%20send%20Rs%2025%2C000%20back%20home.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20keep%20doing%20this%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can.%20If%20not%2C%20tell%20me%2C%20what%20other%20options%20do%20I%20have%3F%E2%80%9D%20Roy%20asks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20passengers%20speak%20up.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20elections%2C%20the%20political%20parties%20come%20calling%2C%20offering%20free%20transportation%20and%20daily%20wages%20just%20for%20attending%20their%20rallies.%20They%20disappear%20after%20the%20elections%20are%20over%2C%20and%20no%20one%20remembers%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20summary%20of%20what%20many%20say.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThroughout%20the%20journey%2C%20passengers%20are%20glued%20to%20their%20phones%2C%20offering%20reassurance%20to%20their%20families%20and%20pledging%20to%20keep%20them%20updated%20once%20they%20arrive%20at%20their%20destination.%20A%20ticket%20to%20this%20train%20was%20a%20ticket%20to%20a%20better%20and%20brighter%20future%20for%20many%20of%20its%20travellers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20night%20wears%20on%2C%20passengers%20become%20friends.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20finish%20all%20the%20food%20at%20once%2C%20we%20still%20have%20a%20day%20or%20three%20to%20sit%20through%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20one.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya%2C%20who%20also%20contributed%20inputs%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695432659000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22171027%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-5.09.51.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Faboard-the-karmabhumi-express-a-reporter-learns-of-the-dreams-of-bengals-outbound-migrants%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Finding%20a%20seat%20on%20this%20train%20for%20migrant%20workers%20is%20close%20to%20impossible.%20A%20closer%20look%20at%20why%20so%20many%20travel%20on%20it%2C%20and%20out%20of%20Bengal%2C%20offers%20a%20grim%20picture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Faboard-the-karmabhumi-express-a-reporter-learns-of-the-dreams-of-bengals-outbound-migrants%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20Intergenerational%2C%20Interfaith%20Family%20and%20an%20Instagram%20Love%20Project%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2F28001656%2Fwedding-marriage-interfaith.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20man%20my%20mother%20chose%20to%20marry%20failed%20to%20check%20the%20conventional%20boxes.%20She%20came%20from%20a%20middle-class%20Parsi%20family%3B%20he%20was%20a%20Tamilian%20Hindu.%20She%20had%20eight%20siblings%20and%20a%20large%20extended%20family%2C%20he%20was%20parentless%20and%20mostly%20without%20a%20family.%20His%20mother%20and%20sibling%20had%20died%20of%20smallpox%20when%20he%20was%20one%2C%20and%20was%20raised%20by%20grand-aunts%20and%20grandparents%2C%20unaware%20of%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20whereabouts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20Indian%20families%20are%20obsessed%20with%20marriage.%20By%20and%20large%2C%20parents%20tend%20to%20control%20the%20process%20for%20their%20children%2C%20beginning%20with%20the%20selection%20of%20a%20partner%20right%20down%20to%20the%20details%20of%20the%20ceremony%20and%20celebrations.%20This%20is%20true%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%20and%20also%20the%20India%20of%20half-a-century%20ago%20when%20my%20parents%20got%20married.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20a%20long%20struggle%20trying%20to%20get%20her%20family%20to%20accept%20her%20choice%20of%20partner%2C%20my%20mother%20walked%20out%20of%20her%20maternal%20home%20on%20her%20wedding%20day.%20With%20their%20close%20friends%20supporting%20them%2C%20my%20parents%20started%20a%20new%20life%20together%20without%20the%20sanction%20or%20support%20of%20relatives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGrowing%20up%20with%20a%20multicultural%20name%20in%20a%20multicultural%20family%2C%20speaking%20mostly%20English%20at%20home%20was%20my%20normal.%20Learning%20about%20the%20Zoroastrian%20religion%20and%20reciting%20prayers%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAvestan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20even%20though%20I%20was%20not%20officially%20initiated%20into%20the%20religion%2C%20was%20my%20reality.%20I%20was%20exposed%20to%20many%20interfaith%20marriages%20and%20adoptions%20from%20the%20time%20I%20was%20very%20young%2C%20and%20perhaps%20because%20of%20that%2C%20I%20never%20felt%20there%20was%20anything%20unusual%20or%20uncommon%20about%20our%20family%20or%20my%20parents%E2%80%99%20choices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fthe-dangerous-agenda-behind-probing-interfaith-marriages%5C%22%3EThe%20Dangerous%20Agenda%20Behind%20Probing%20Interfaith%20Marriages%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYears%20later%2C%20when%20I%20married%20someone%20from%20a%20faith%20different%20from%20both%20my%20parents%2C%20it%20was%20never%20a%20discussion%20at%20home.%20It%20was%20only%20in%20my%2020s%2C%20when%20friends%20had%20trouble%20trying%20to%20exercise%20their%20personal%20choice%20to%20be%20with%20a%C2%A0%20partner%20from%20a%20different%20religion%2C%20that%20it%20struck%20me%20that%20my%20parents%E2%80%99%20marriage%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20as%20ordinary%20as%20I%20had%20thought.%20It%20surprises%20me%20that%2C%20even%20today%2C%20people%20make%20comments%20about%20my%20name%20and%20assume%20that%20I%20must%20have%20gotten%20my%20surname%20from%20my%20spouse.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%2C%20we%20increasingly%20hear%20that%20we%20must%20stick%20to%20our%20caste%2Freligion%2Fkind%20and%20that%20love%20or%20a%20relationship%20outside%20these%20narrow%20fields%20is%20illegitimate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20All%20around%20us%2C%20we%20see%20this%20wave%20of%20hate%20that%20demonises%20interfaith%2C%20intercaste%2C%20and%20LGBTQIA%2B%20relationships.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Priya%20Ramani%2C%20Samar%20Halarnkar%2C%20and%20I%20started%20the%20India%20Love%20Project%20(ILP)*%20in%202020%2C%20it%20was%20our%20way%20of%20celebrating%20unconventional%20love.%20As%20journalists%2C%20we%20responded%20in%20the%20way%20we%20knew%20best%3A%20with%20a%20storytelling%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20354px)%2085vw%2C%20354px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22134620%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-1.45.40-PM-300x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22354%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22134620%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-1.45.40-PM-300x300.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22134620%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-1.45.40-PM-1022x1024.png%201022w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22134620%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-1.45.40-PM-150x150.png%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22134620%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-1.45.40-PM.png%201134w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674309%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22354%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Instagram%2F%40indialoveproject%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThrough%20ILP%2C%20we%20share%20the%20idea%20that%20many%20kinds%20of%20non-conforming%20relationships%20thrive%2C%20various%20combinations%20make%20up%20families%2C%20and%20our%20world%20is%20a%20plural%20and%20diverse%20place.%20As%20a%20product%20of%20an%20interfaith%20marriage%20myself%2C%20I%20feel%20that%20this%20is%20very%20personal%20%E2%80%93%20we%E2%80%99re%20saying%20we%20do%20exist%2C%20and%20thousands%20of%20couples%20continue%20to%20make%20that%20choice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20interest%20in%20divisiveness%20and%20those%20who%20try%20to%20counter%20it%20is%20not%20new.%20In%20my%20doctoral%20dissertation%20in%201998%2C%20I%20talked%20about%20the%20communal%20riots%20of%20the%201990s%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20hatred.%20I%20focused%20on%20the%20strategies%2C%20tactics%2C%20and%20various%20initiatives%20to%20fight%20the%20divisive%20narrative%20being%20nurtured%20in%20those%20times%20and%20researched%20small%20activist%20groups%20fighting%20communalism.%20I%20recall%20how%20Maruti%2C%20a%20young%20social%20worker%20and%20activist%20rallying%20against%20the%20communal%20discourse%2C%20echoing%20Ambedkar%2C%20once%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20way%20we%20can%20fight%20this%20is%20if%20we%20all%20marry%20someone%20outside%20our%20religion%20or%20caste.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to.%E2%80%9D%20I%20wonder%20if%20he%20found%20a%20partner%20outside%20the%20tightly%20drawn%20lines%20of%20caste%20and%20religion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20my%20friend%20and%20ILP%20co-founder%20Priya%20has%20long%20been%20obsessed%20with%20talking%20about%20interfaith%20love.%20In%C2%A0%20many%20of%20her%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flifestyle.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Ftalking-point%2Fmy-letter-to-alia-malia-jamalia-111646992861887.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecolumns%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20dating%20back%20from%202015%2C%20she%20addresses%20the%20question%3A%20How%20many%20times%20have%20we%20been%20told%20that%20our%20youth%20are%20not%20okay%20with%20inter-religious%20friendships%20or%20relationships%3F%20Priya%20has%20often%20talked%20about%20the%20right%20to%20choose.%20She%20says%20that%20her%20journey%20through%20north%20India%20with%20Harsh%20Mander%E2%80%99s%20Karwan-e-Mohabbat%20in%202017%20only%20made%20her%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20worlds%20of%20love%20and%20hate%20through%20her%20writing.%20Just%20a%20cursory%20search%20through%20her%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flifestyle.livemint.com%2Frelationships%2Fit-s-complicated%2Fthe-year-of-love-and-hate-111646913630772.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecolumns%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20throws%20up%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FOpinion%2FuwVngLAkk1xjrzaJiEKCJL%2FLove-as-a-response-to-lynching.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eover%20a%20dozen%20instances%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20where%20she%E2%80%99s%20discussed%20the%20topic%20between%202015%20and%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESamar%E2%80%99s%20connection%20to%20this%20issue%20began%20when%20he%20was%20a%20child%20and%20watched%20his%20parents%20counsel%20some%20of%20their%20best%20friends%2C%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%2C%20when%20their%20children%20chose%20Hindu%20partners.%20Always%20fascinated%20by%20the%20idea%20of%20love%20beyond%20traditional%20barriers%2C%20he%20was%20dismayed%20when%20the%20bogus%20concept%20of%20love%20jihad%20gained%20ground%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-interface-of-love-and-jihad-is-a-false-indian-articulation%5C%22%3EThe%20Interface%20of%20%E2%80%98Love%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Jihad%E2%80%99%20Is%20a%20False%20Indian%20Articulation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20a%20long%20time%20Samar%20had%20been%20suggesting%20creating%20a%20website%20that%20shares%20such%20love%20stories%20and%20offers%20counselling%20and%20legal%20services%20to%20interfaith%20couples.%20In%202020%2C%20in%20response%20to%20the%20hate-mongering%20over%20an%20ad%20celebrating%20an%20interfaith%20relationship%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20go%20with%20a%20more%20millennial-friendly%20approach%20and%20took%20to%20sharing%20stories%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20launched%20ILP%2C%20we%20knew%20we%20wanted%20to%20go%20beyond%20that%20original%20idea%20of%20interfaith%20couples%20to%20share%20real-life%20stories%20of%20couples%20that%20broke%20the%20barriers%20of%20not%20just%20faith%20but%20caste%2C%20race%2C%20and%20gender.%20We%20wanted%20these%20stories%20to%20tell%20the%20world%20that%20the%20best%20way%20to%20counter%20narrow%2C%20hateful%20or%20fake%20narratives%20is%20to%20share%20those%C2%A0%20of%20diversity%2C%20hope%2C%20and%20love.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20329px)%2085vw%2C%20329px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22134906%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-1.48.49-PM-285x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22329%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22134906%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-1.48.49-PM-285x300.png%20285w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22134906%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-1.48.49-PM-972x1024.png%20972w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22134906%2FScreenshot-2023-09-22-at-1.48.49-PM.png%201114w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674310%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22346%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Instagram%2F%40indialoveproject%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20child%20of%20an%20interfaith%20couple%20in%20an%20interfaith%20marriage%2C%20sharing%20these%20stories%20also%20helps%20us%20say%20%E2%80%9Cwe%E2%80%99re%20here%2C%20we%20cannot%20be%20wished%20away%2C%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20absolutely%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20relationships%20that%20cut%20across%20majoritarian%20expectations%E2%80%9D.%20We%20point%20out%20that%20interfaith%20and%20other%20non-mainstream%20relationships%20have%20been%20in%20India%20for%20decades%3B%20they%20continue%20and%20will%20likely%20expand%2C%20especially%20as%20young%20people%20migrate%20in%20search%20of%20education%20and%20work.%20We%20want%20to%20emphasise%20that%20the%20relationships%20they%20may%20have%20are%20not%20anomalies%20or%20deviant%20behaviour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20us%2C%20ILP%C2%A0%20is%20important%20because%20it%20is%20a%20happy%20space%20that%20speaks%20to%20a%20plural%20and%20inclusive%20society.%20Who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20like%20a%20good%20love%20story%3F%20When%20people%20read%20about%20how%20someone%20found%20love%20and%20managed%20to%20exercise%20the%20freedom%20to%20choose%20and%20love%20a%20person%20of%20their%20choice%2C%20it%20is%20reassuring%2C%20comforting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20right%20to%20choose%20is%20central%20to%20ILP%E2%80%99s%20narrative.%20In%20a%20country%20obsessed%20with%20marriage%20and%20weddings%2C%20we%20intend%20to%20continue%20telling%20alternative%20real-life%20stories%20to%20spread%20the%20message%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20selecting%20your%20own%20partner.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20many%20couples%2C%20s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eharing%20their%20love%20stories%20is%20therapeutic%2C%20a%20release.%20If%20more%20and%20more%20people%20tell%20their%20stories%20about%20different%20expressions%20of%20choice%20%E2%80%93%20on%20social%20media%2C%20in%20films%2C%20in%20books%2C%20in%20whatever%20way%20they%20can%20%E2%80%93%20it%20will%20only%20give%20young%20lovers%20hope.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENiloufer%20Venkatraman%20is%20one%20of%20three%20co-founders%20of%20India%20Love%20Project%20(%40indialoveproject).%20She%20is%20Consulting%20Editor%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Froundglasssustain.com%5C%22%3ERoundGlass%20Sustain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20wildlife%20and%20conservation%20website%20documenting%20India%E2%80%99s%20species%20and%20habitats%20and%20their%20preservation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E*As%20the%20India%20Love%20Project%20(ILP)%20is%20one%20of%2010%20fi