20this%20profound%20question%20surfaced%20after%20dedicating%20more%20than%2015%20years%20of%20his%20life%20to%20serving%20his%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20have%20either%20been%20living%20in%20the%20past%20or%20in%20the%20future.%20For%20once%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20the%20present%20and%20find%20what%20I%20want%20to%20focus%20on%20next%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Major%20Vivek%20(44)%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDesiring%20a%20respite%20from%20the%20demands%20of%20life%20and%20yearning%20to%20%E2%80%9Csit%20on%20a%20mountain%2C%20read%20books%2C%20and%20disconnect%20from%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Major%20Vivek%20Jacob%20contemplated%20early%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20given%20my%20country%20and%20my%20work%20all%20that%20I%20could.%20I%20knew%20it%20was%20time%20for%20me%20to%20move%20on%20to%20a%20different%20facet%20of%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20However%2C%20as%20unpredictable%20as%20life%20can%20be%2C%20this%20choice%20took%20the%20major%20down%20a%20path%20he%20may%20have%20never%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20he%20runs%20an%20organisation%20called%20CLAW%20Global%20(Conquer%20Land%2C%20Air%2C%20Water)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20social%20impact%20venture%20working%20towards%20the%20rehabilitation%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306209%2Fbengaluru-ngo-gives-horticulture-training-to-people-with-disability-provides-job-placements%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20people%20with%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20way%20of%20sports.%20Major%20Jacob%20not%20only%20trains%20them%20but%20also%20leads%20them%20on%20exhilarating%20adventures%2C%20such%20as%20scuba%20diving%2C%20sky%20diving%2C%20and%20mountaineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20prompted%20this%20profound%20shift%20from%20seeking%20respite%20to%20founding%20an%20organisation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20military%20service%20to%20empowering%20the%20disabled%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20part%20of%209%20Para%20Special%20Forces%2C%20in%202015%2C%20Major%20Vivek%20met%20with%20an%20accident%20while%20training%20and%20injured%20his%20spine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20he%20met%20Flight%20Lieutenant%20Bhaduria%20who%20was%20paralysed%20waist%20down%20for%20the%20last%20four%20years%20due%20to%20an%20accident.%20The%20lieutenant%20had%20dived%20into%20a%20pool%20and%20hit%20his%20head%2C%20injuring%20his%20neck%20which%20left%20him%20paralysed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20time%20in%20the%20military%20hospital%2C%20as%20I%20recovered%2C%20I%20closely%20observed%20how%20hard%20my%20friend%E2%80%99s%20life%20was.%20He%20was%20suffering%20and%20losing%20hope%20in%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCTsIGnpIHeu%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCTsIGnpIHeu%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E