%20so%20moved%20by%20the%20cuisines%20that%20I%20learnt%20to%20cook%20them%20from%20Vinod%20and%20his%20mom%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20she%20decided%20to%20introduce%20it%20to%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20anatomy%20of%20Onam%20%3Cem%3Esadhya%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnam%20is%20the%20biggest%20festival%20celebrated%20across%20Kerala%20to%20commemorate%20the%20return%20of%20the%20mythical%20King%20Mahabali.%20The%20story%20goes%20that%20he%20was%20banished%20to%20the%20land%20of%20the%20dead%20by%20Lord%20Vishnu%20but%20was%20granted%20the%20privilege%20of%20returning%20to%20his%20beloved%20state%20once%20a%20year%20during%20Onam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%2010-day%20festival%2C%20the%20whole%20family%20gets%20together%20for%20a%20grand%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F113931%2F10-days-onam-pookalams-onasadhya-heres-need-know%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evegetarian%20feast%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20the%20Onam%20%3Cem%3Esadhya%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Traditionally%20served%20on%20a%20banana%20leaf%20and%20eaten%20by%20hand%2C%20it%20comprises%20dozens%20of%20dishes%20including%20rice%2C%20curries%20like%20%3Cem%3Ethoran%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eavial%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20desserts%20like%20the%20creamy%20%3Cem%3Epayasam%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20a%20sweet%20pudding%20cooked%20in%20coconut%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FThattu-1695302803.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sadhya%20is%20traditionally%20served%20on%20a%20banana%20leaf%20and%20comprises%20dozens%20of%20dishes%20including%20rice%2C%20curries%2C%20and%20desserts.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-med