0of%20Chandigarh.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20this%20job%20very%20useful%20as%20I%20was%20able%20to%20serve%20my%20cause%20and%20also%20earn%20some%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20his%20daily%20schedule%2C%20irrespective%20of%20office%20hours%2C%20he%20sets%20out%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F278819%2Fdelhi-brothers-rescue-birds-kite-flying-injuries-wildlife-hospital%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erescue%20mission%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebetween%203-11%20pm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLocal%20people%20call%20to%20inform%20me%20about%20injured%20or%20dead%20birds.%20Usually%2C%20these%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277445%2Fdelhi-brothers-rescue-injured-birds-kite-flying-wildlife-clinic%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einnocent%20birds%20%3C%2Fa%3Eget%20wounded%20by%20sharp%20kite%20strings%20or%20from%20fans%20in%20shops.%20In%20summer%2C%20exhausted%20birds%20fall%20from%20the%20sky%20or%20collide%20with%20high-tension%20wires%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%2015-30%20minutes%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20distance%20he%20can%20cover%20on%20his%20bicycle%2C%20Manjit%20rescues%20these%20birds.%20He%20carries%20all%20the%20necessary%20equipment%20and%20medicines%20along%20with%20him.%20This%20includes%20a%20small%20spade%2C%20Negasunt%20powder%20(an%20antibacterial%20used%20for%20dressing%20wounds)%2C%20Bird%20Plus%20syrup%2C%20and%20a%20pair%20of%20scissors%20to%20free%20birds%20from%20tangled%20wires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20bird%20is%20dead%2C%20I%20dig%20a%201.5%20ft%20hole%20and%20bury%20it%20in%20an%20open%20ground%20in%20the%20city.%20If%20the%20bird%20requires%20stitches%20or%20is%20critical%2C%20I%20take%20it%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20treatment.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20minor%20injury%2C%20I%20take%20them%20to%20my%20house%20where%20I%20feed%20them%20and%20after%20they%20get%20well%2C%20I%20set%20them%20free%20in%202-5%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-5-1695045299.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manjit%20has%20treated%201%2C160%20birds%20so%20far.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-5-1695045299.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-5-1695045299-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-5-1695045299-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-5-1695045299-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmanjit-singh-5-1695045299-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330218%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManjit%20has%20treated%201%2C160%20birds%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20aid%20his%20work%2C%20a%20bank%20donated%20a%20battery-operated%20bike%20to%20Manjit%20in%202012.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20giving%20me%20a%20scooter%20as%20I%20travel%20throughout%20the%20day.%20But%20I%20refused%20it%20because%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20weaken%20my%20mission%20to%20reduce%20air%20pollution%20just%20because%20I%20was%20getting%20a%20free%20scooter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20battery-powered%20bike%20helps%20me%20reach%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F34754%2Frescue-birds-jaipur-raksha-rohit-gangwal-kite-flying%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einjured%20birds%20%3C%2Fa%3Efast.%20If%20the%20bird%20is%20already%20dead%2C%20I%20then%20use%20my%20usual%20bicycle%20to%20reach%20the%20place%20and%20bury%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecalling%20a%20busy%20day%2C%20Manjit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CLast%20year%2C%20a%20storm%20hit%20the%20city%20and%20several%20trees%20fell%20in%20the%20night.%20These%20trees%20were%20home%20to%20numerous%20parrots.%20I%20received%20a%20call%20at%206am%20to%20collect%20250%20dead%20parrots%20and%2080%20pigeons.%20All%20in%20one%20day.%20The%20two%20baskets%20attached%20to%20my%20bicycle%20were%20full%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRecently%2C%20I%20rescued%20five%20parrots%20whose%20feet%20were%20damaged.%20I%20kept%20them%20on%20treatment%20in%20my%20house%20for%20two%20months%20before%20they%20got%20better%20and%20could%20fly%20off.%20Currently%2C%20I%20have%20two%20pigeons%20and%20one%20%3Cem%3Eghuggi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(turtle%20dove)%20at%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20work%2C%20Manjit%20keeps%20aside%2020%20percent%20of%20his%20salary.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20have%20offered%20a%20fee%20for%20this%20work%2C%20I%20request%20them%20to%20instead%20pay%20me%20in%20kind%20and%20provide%20bird%20feed%20like%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%20%3C%2Fem%3E(pearl%20millet)%20for%20the%20injured%20birds.%20If%20I%20start%20asking%20money%20for%20it%2C%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20%3Cem%3Esewa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(service)%2C%20it%20will%20become%20a%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20dead%20birds%20are%20stuck%20to%20the%20road%2C%20and%20people%20cover%20their%20noses%20with%20a%20cloth%2C%20but%20I%20have%20to%20pick%20them%20so%20that%20they%20are%20buried%20safely.%20Initially%2C%20my%20family%20opposed%20my%20decision%20due%20to%20this%20very%20reason%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EPar%20woh%20jeena%20kya%20jeena%20jo%20apne%20liye%20jiyein%20%3C%2Fem%3E(There%E2%80%99s%20no%20point%2