ut%20that%20there%20was%20a%20death%20in%20their%20family%2010%20days%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20two%20of%20the%20children%2C%20a%2049-year-old%2C%20had%20died%20in%20another%20hospital%20nearby.%20Interestingly%2C%20all%20patients%20hailed%20from%20Maruthonkara%2C%20which%20was%20near%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20Nipah%20virus%20outbreak%20in%20Kerala%20in%202018.%20This%20worried%20the%20treating%20team%2C%20which%20included%20Dr%20Anoop%20Kumar%20AS%20who%20is%20the%20director%20of%20North%20Kerala%20(Cluster)%20of%20Critical%20Care%20Medicine%20at%20the%20Aster%20Hospitals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENipah%20is%20a%20zoonotic%20virus%20that%20spreads%20from%20infected%20animals%20like%20bats%20or%20pigs%20to%20humans.%20Dr%20Kumar%20has%20also%20been%20credited%20for%20catching%20the%20first%20Nipah%20outbreak%20in%202018%20in%20time.%20His%20quick%20thinking%20and%20swift%20action%20helped%20the%20patients%20back%20then%20and%20are%20showing%20the%20same%20effect%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20clustering%20of%20cases%20with%20respiratory%20symptoms%2C%20coupled%20with%20a%20probable%20index%20(primary)%20case%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20hail%20from%20the%20area%20near%20the%20previous%20epicentre%2C%20gave%20us%20a%20suspicion%20that%20it%20was%20a%20rare%20virus%20and%20that%20it%20could%20be%20Nipah%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Kumar%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20of%20doctors%20acted%20quickly%20by%20isolating%20these%20four%20patients%20and%20sent%20their%20samples%20to%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Virology%20(NIV)%2C%20Pune.%20They%20also%20informed%20the%20state%20health%20authorities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20sudden%20death%20on%2011%20September%20of%20a%2042-year-old%20patient%20with%20similar%20symptoms%20but%20in%20a%20different%20hospital%20kept%20the%20doctors%20suspicious.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETracing%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%3Cstrong%3E%20disease%20route%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20837px)%20100vw%2C%20837px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fdr-anoop-kumar-as-1694787970.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22837%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Anoop%20Kumar%20AS%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fdr-anoop-kumar-as-1694787970.jpeg%20837w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fdr-anoop-kumar-as-1694787970-241x300.jpeg%20241w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fdr-anoop-kumar-as-1694787970-500x623.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fdr-anoop-kumar-as-1694787970-768x957.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fdr-anoop-kumar-as-1694787970-150x187.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330118%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221043%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Anoop%20Kumar%20AS%20helped%20diagnose%20Nipah%20Virus%20in%202018%20and%202023%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20started%20probing%20the%20death%20of%20the%20kids%E2%80%99%20father.%20The%20initial%20reports%20said%20that%20he%20died%20of%20bronchopneumonia%20and%20multi-organ%20failure.%20However%2C%20on%20reanalysis%2C%20we%20found%20that%20he%20had%20unusual%20symptoms%20like%20slurring%20of%20speech%2C%20diplopia%20(double%20vision)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Kumar%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20his%20nine-year-old%20elder%20son%2C%20who%20was%20admitted%20with%20severe%20breathing%20difficulties%2C%20started%20developing%20convulsions%20and%20was%20put%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the